  1. County Highlights

  1. Big Jazz Sound

    Enjoy concerts in an intimate setting all Spring. The acoustics make every show a special moment. Check out local and national artists at the Montpelier Arts Center. Online tickets available. See Schedule

  2. Spring Into Action

    Each Spring and Fall, we host a county-wide cleanup program. Come support our initiative to make our community cleaner, greener, and beautiful. Learn How

  3. Books from Birth

    There is nothing like giving your child a head-start in enjoying books. When you sign up your child, they will receive a FREE book in the mail monthly until their 5th birthday. Learn More

  4. It's Showtime!

    Since 1947, Publick Playhouse has served as popular spot for the performing arts. Known for its comfy space and great acoustics, this historic theater is one of the best venues in the area. See Events
